sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant FE as Web Frontend
    participant API as PasswordController
    participant P as PasswordApplicationService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis
    participant T as TokenService
    participant A as Audit Platform

    U->>FE: change password; optionally select logout all devices
    FE->>API: POST /password/change
    API->>P: changePassword(currentSession, oldPassword, newPassword, logoutAll)
    P->>DB: verify user and current credential
    P->>P: validate old password and new password policy
    P->>DB: BEGIN
    P->>DB: update credential hash
    P->>DB: securityVersion++
    P->>DB: COMMIT
    alt logoutAll selected
        P->>R: revoke all sessions including current
        P->>R: create fresh session for current device
        P->>T: issue fresh tokens
        P->>A: logout.all.devices.after.password.update
        P-->>API: fresh tokens
    else logoutAll not selected
        P->>R: revoke other sessions per configured password-change policy
        P->>R: refresh/recreate current session with new securityVersion
        P->>T: issue fresh tokens
        P-->>API: fresh tokens
    end
    API-->>FE: success
